cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper focuses on visual-inertial odometry and depth map estimation using self-supervised deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it deals with ego-motion estimation and sensor fusion. The use of deep learning and adversarial training suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves system engineering and control (cs.SY) as it deals with sensor fusion and estimation.
